    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]

) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]

LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

To identify the query that's triggering this warning call 'ConfigureWarnings(w => w.Throw(RelationalEventId.MultipleCollectionIncludeWarning))'.

FROM [Tours] AS [t]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]

    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]

SELECT [t0].[Id], [t0].[Capacity], [t0].[CountryCount], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Desc], [t0].[Duration], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[Image], [t0].[Name], [t0].[OldPrice], [t0].[Price], [t0].[StartDate], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[CountryId], [t1].[CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name], [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [t3].[Id0], [t3].[CreatedDate0], [t3].[Name], [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [t5].[Id0], [t5].[CreatedDate0], [t5].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate]
    FROM [Tours] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t0]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t2].[Id], [t2].[CityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t2]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t2].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[Id] = [t1].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t4].[Id], [t4].[ActivityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t4]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t4].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t3] ON [t0].[Id] = [t3].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t6].[Id], [t6].[AmenityId], [t6].[CreatedDate], [t6].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t6]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t6].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t5] ON [t0].[Id] = [t5].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t0].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t0].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t5].[Id], [t5].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

    WHERE [t].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t0]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t2].[Id], [t2].[CityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]

) AS [t5] ON [t0].[Id] = [t5].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]

) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate]
    FROM [Tours] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t0]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t2].[Id], [t2].[CityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t2]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t2].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[Id] = [t1].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t4].[Id], [t4].[ActivityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t4]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t4].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t3] ON [t0].[Id] = [t3].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t6].[Id], [t6].[AmenityId], [t6].[CreatedDate], [t6].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t6]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t6].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t5] ON [t0].[Id] = [t5].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t0].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t0].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t5].[Id], [t5].[Id0], [e].[Id]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]

    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]

    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

2025-06-28 13:25:29.408 +04:00 [INF] Route matched with {action = "GetAll", controller = "Tour"}. Executing controller action with signature System.Threading.Tasks.Task`1[Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.IActionResult] GetAll() on controller FinalProject.Controllers.Admin.TourController (FinalProject).
2025-06-28 13:25:29.410 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

2025-06-28 13:33:40.023 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (20ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]

    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

2025-06-28 17:02:38.477 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[Name0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c0] ON [c].[CountryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]

    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]

) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]
